item.title: RIP a Livecast #721 - Dehydrated Apricot
item.description: We kick things off by discussing David Ellefson's controversial comments about Dave Mustaine recently. We compare this to Jason Newsted defending his former bandmate, Lars Ulrich. Then, we can't help ourselves and play some of the most outlandish moments of the Trump town hall. Transitioning to another WWE Hall of Famer, we check in and see what Hulk Hogan and his son Nick are up to... Feed: https://feeds.acast.com/public/shows/638fae377944c60011e2e293

item.title: Wrong Turn Proves Fatal for Garuda Indonesia Flight 152
item.description: Chris Demarais and Gustavo Sorola uncover how a wrong turn became deadly for Garuda Indonesia Flight 152 on this episode of Black Box Down. Feed: https://feeds.megaphone.fm/blackboxdown
